00:53:59.982 --> 00:54:01.152
(Si Ms. Ok Rye ay isang grupo ng nerbiyos.)

00:54:01.212 --> 00:54:02.852
Isa, dalawa,

00:54:03.152 --> 00:54:07.052
- tatlo, apat, lima. - Nasa isang fashion show?

00:54:07.452 --> 00:54:08.792
Hinihiling mo ba sa akin na maging modelo?

00:54:09.352 --> 00:54:13.122
- Nakuha ni Lola ang kanyang unang trabaho bilang modelo. - Kaliwang bahagi, pose.

00:54:13.792 --> 00:54:15.492
Kanang bahagi, magpose.

00:54:15.792 --> 00:54:19.702
Kanang paa! Lumiko at mag-pose.

00:54:20.432 --> 00:54:22.472
(Ang Malaking Araw: Ang Palabas ng Moda)

00:54:23.372 --> 00:54:25.842
Maniniwala ka bang lola ko 'yan?

00:54:25.902 --> 00:54:27.242
